{"tid":862353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港差得過Gotham咩？","createTime":"2018-10-14T18:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T00:12:33.000Z","uid":4320,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a02c218008aefd396c027d83f3f5dbf7c11bd8e8","tid":862353,"uid":4320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:33:08.000Z","msg":"對唔住又開多個post<br />\n但我見得太多巴打話灰話無希望話移民<br />\n我係一個蝙蝠俠迷<br />\n佢個種正義感同犧牲精神令我十分尊敬<br />\n作為一個億萬富豪<br />\n見到個城市咁垃圾<br />\n好心地d既就捐下錢幫下窮人<br />\n再唔係就拍拍羅友走啦<br />\n點解要不眠不休咁打擊罪案？<br />\n我地唔係蝙蝠俠<br />\n我地好多都係窮撚<br />\n但當個城市仲未墮落到好似Gotham咁既時候點解我地反而要放棄？<br />\n我地仲有能力對抗個政權<br />\n但如果我地宜家灰，放棄<br />\n當香港真係變到Gotham咁既時候<br />\n咁就唯有真係等蝙蝠俠打救我地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef82424b4639efc81c86324605f90b987884f04","tid":862353,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:36:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed7647072e5449395b805993b6a6150086f295f4","tid":862353,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T23:22:21.000Z","msg":"有錢做蝙蝠俠，<br />\n無錢做咩呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253778d9ade435971e70c22ada7d51ee049fb792","tid":862353,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T23:27:54.000Z","msg":"其實美國係人工島依件事上面可以點幫手?中國本來就準備同美國打貿易戰,中國唔會怕美國制裁掛<br />\n小弟唔係好識政治,有冇人可以解釋下?"},{"pid":"c95930e7562b0cce0b3af85eb7b8fe10e0237b71","tid":862353,"uid":1355,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T23:30:35.000Z","msg":"香港如果有呢個情況嘅話，我覺得兩架船都會爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/15/073030_63f92c48618574f2a271c2fb27c6a967.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F15%2F073030_63f92c48618574f2a271c2fb27c6a967.png&h=f1cc3f13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b81391add15edb1794b622749a74f9779